revision.text:
{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2013}}

The '''2007 [[Libyan SuperCup]]''' took place between [[Libyan Premier League 2006-07|2006-07]] [[Libyan Premier League]] champions [[Al Ittihad Tripoli|Al Ittihad]] and the 2007 [[Libyan Cup]] runners-up [[Al Akhdar]] (Al Ittihad won the Libyan Cup, so Al Akhdar took their place in the competition as cup runners-up). This was the 11th edition of the competition, and the match ended 3-1 to Al Ittihad after extra time. This was Al Ittihad's 6th consecutive win in the competition.

