'''Afghanistan''' competed at the '''[[2008 Asian Beach Games|2008]] [[Asian Beach Games]]''' held in [[Bali]], [[Indonesia]] from October 18, 2008 to October 26, 2008. Afghanistan finished with 1 gold medal and 1 bronze medal. Both medals were won in the sport of [[Beach wrestling at the 2008 Asian Beach Games|beach wrestling]]
