==={{flagicon|Ireland}} Ireland=== In Ireland, the double is achieved by winning the [[League of Ireland]] and [[FAI Cup]]. Bohemians managed a similar feat in 1928 season by winning the [[League of Ireland|League]], [[FAI Cup]], the [[League of Ireland Shield]] and the [[Leinster Senior Cup (association football)|Leinster Senior Cup]]. [[Derry City FC]] completed '[[The Treble#Domestic Treble|The Treble]]' in 1988–89 by also winning the League of Ireland Cup.
