==={{flagicon|Israel}} Israel=== In [[Israel]], the Double can be achieved by winning the [[List of Israeli football champions|Top division championship]] and the [[Israel State Cup]]. The team that has won the most doubles to date is [[Maccabi Tel Aviv F.C.|Maccabi Tel Aviv]], with seven wins, followed by their city rivals, [[Hapoel Tel Aviv F.C.|Hapoel Tel Aviv]] with four wins. A total of 15 doubles have been won.
