==[[N.F.-Board|Other countries]]==
==={{flagicon|Greenland}} Greenland=== The [[Greenlandic Football Championship]] is the only national football competition in the country.
==={{flagicon|Kiribati}} Kiribati=== In [[Kiribati]], there is no national cup; the [[Kiribati National Championship]] is the only national football competition in the country.
==={{flagicon|Northern Cyprus}} Northern Cyprus=== In [[Northern Cyprus]], five teams have won the Double of the [[Birinci Lig]] and the [[Federasyon Kupası|Kıbrıs Kupası/Federasyon Kupası]].
