===League & Cup Winners' Cup Double=== Similarly, there were six occasions of clubs winning their League and the now defunct [[UEFA Cup Winners' Cup]] (CWC). No club ever won the CWC as part of a recognised treble. In the case of [[1. FC Magdeburg]] and [[FC Dynamo Kyiv|Dynamo Kyiv]], it is also worth noting that the domestic Championships they won are also now disbanded, due to [[German reunification]] and the [[Dissolution of the Soviet Union|disintegration of the Soviet Union]] respectively.
