==Cup Double== There are various possible combinations of winning two knock-out competitions.
===Domestic Cup Double=== A Domestic Cup Double consists of winning both domestic cup competitions in a single season or calendar year (for seasons when this double was won in conjunction with the league title see [[The Treble#Domestic Treble|Domestic Treble]]). Examples include:
