[[File:Kenny Serracin.jpg|250px|thumb|Estadio Kenny Serracín]]
{{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}}
'''Estadio Kenny Serracín''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[David, Panama|David]], [[Panama]].  It is currently used for [[baseball]] matches and is the home stadium of Chiriquí baseball team.  The stadium holds 2,000 people.

==History==

Used to be called Estadio 3 de noviembre until 1976.<br>
[[Atletico Chiriqui]] soccer team used to play before the construction of<br>
San Cristobal soccer field.

