The '''Stade el-Massira''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Safi, Morocco|Safi]], [[Morocco]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and hosts the home games of [[Olympique Safi]].  The stadium holds 15,000 people.<ref>{{cite web|title=Stade El Massira|accessdate=18 August 2017|publisher=soccerway|url=https://int.soccerway.com/venues/morocco/stade-el-massira/v7211/}}</ref>

